content.rendered:
The Evaluate Industrial Steel Side Chair is a commercial grade classroom-look chair perfect for industrial themes or those looking for a strong, care-free Side Chair.

Held in stock in a black steel frame with an oak veneered seat and backrest.

Some self assembly may be required. Stackable 4 high.
